Ghana abatoɔ wɔ Ghana no kɔɔ so wɔ December a ɛtɔ so 7, afe 2004. Manpanyin abatoɔ a ɛkɔɔ so no maa John Kufour a odi ɔyɛ manpanin no a odi amanyɔkuo New Patriotic Party (NPP) anim dii nkunim. Mmarahye bagua abtoɔ no maa amanyɔkuo NPP no nyaa agua a ne dodo no yɛ 230 no mu 128.

== Manpanyin abatoɔ no ==
ɔperetiafo dodoɔ nnan na ɛkɔɔ abatoɔ no mu a wɔn ne; 

* [[George Aggudey]] ([[CPP|Convention People's Party]])
* [[John Kofi Agyekum Kufuor|John Kufuor]] ([[NPP|New Patriotic Party]]) - incumbent
* [[John Atta Mills]] ([[NDC|National Democratic Congress]])
* Edward Mahama (Grand Coalition, nkabom aban a People's National Convention, Every Ghanaian Living Everywhere, ne Great Consolidated Popular Party)

